# Phase 5: Booking Flow — Implementation Plan

> **Phase:** 5 of 8
> **Owner:** Product Engineer (Beloved)
> **Estimated Time:** ~3 hours
> **Depends on:** Phase 4B complete (gallery, style detail, stylist profile pages)
> **Design Reference:** `design/booking flow/` (Stitch mockup)

---

## Overview

The booking flow is the conversion point where users commit to a hairstyle appointment. This page must:
1. Display the selected style and stylist information
2. Allow date and time slot selection
3. Capture client location (for mobile stylists)
4. Show price breakdown with booking fee
5. Create a pending booking record and redirect to payment

---

## Design Requirements (from Stitch Mockup)

| Element | Specification |
|---------|---------------|
| **Layout** | Two-column on desktop (calendar left, time/location right), single column mobile |
| **Header** | Style image (3:4 ratio), style name (Playfair italic), price, stylist card |
| **Service Toggle** | Pill toggle: "Salon Visit" / "Home Service" |
| **Calendar** | Custom glassmorphism calendar with gold selected state, month navigation |
| **Time Slots** | Morning (8am-12pm), Afternoon (12pm-5pm), Evening (5pm-9pm) with icons |
| **Location** | Address input with map preview (gold pin marker) |
| **Price Summary** | Service price + ₦500 booking fee = Total |
| **CTA** | "Proceed to Payment" — gradient gold button |

