## Verification Checklist

- [ ] Booking page loads with correct style and stylist data
- [ ] Calendar shows correct month, disables past dates
- [ ] Time slots are selectable with visual feedback
- [ ] Location input only appears for home service
- [ ] Price summary calculates correctly
- [ ] Form validation prevents submit without required fields
- [ ] Booking is created in Supabase with pending status
- [ ] Redirect to payment page works with booking ID
- [ ] Mobile responsive layout matches mockup

