## Notes

- **Google Maps API:** Deferred for hackathon. Using static map image placeholder. Can add Places Autocomplete post-MVP.
- **Booking Fee:** Hardcoded at ₦500 per Stitch mockup
- **Confirmation Code:** 4-digit numeric, generated server-side
- **Authentication:** Required for booking. Middleware should redirect unauthenticated users to login.
